              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1 text-center">Alfa Laval Decanter Centrifuge Cross Section</p>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Decanter Centrifuge</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                A <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/" class="text-navy underline hover:text-gold">decanter centrifuge</a> is an industrial centrifuge with a horizontal rotating bowl with a concentric conveyor rotating inside the bowl at a differential speed. The centrifugal force of the rotation causes the solids to settle at the bowl wall from where the conveyor pushes them to the solid outlet ports. The separated liquid moves and exits the bowl from the liquid end on the opposite side.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
